#mommyandme #christmascookies

Y’all…it’s about time. The parlor🥰<<swipe for before>> The Georgian house we bought had some drop dead gorgeous bones camouflaged by outdated everything. After 5 months of covering brown wood, replacing wrought iron fixtures with polished brass, and walking through ladders & boxes…it is starting to look like an Ellinghaus home. 

My favorite thing in the parlor is the restored portrait of my Mom Mom as a teenager above the fireplace in a watercolor…and the @thibaut_1886 curtains and @sherwinwilliams Hinting Blue coffered 12’ ceilings are pretty good too!
